        "timestamp": "2019-06-07 17:28:53.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThanks Jim, is it possible to describe a little the intended behavior at high level here or in ticket? I cannot capture the intent just from the review.  There's a big stretch between undeploy the latest (even if in error from the ticket) vs. undeploying all.   More specifically, I would also like to understand in there are sideeffects for example if there are different versions of same policy in different groups/subgroups deployed at the same time, how it is handled.",
